{"tid":61353,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[富奸肯畫未]Hunter入面比絲姬既真正實力?","createTime":"2016-12-31T07:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T13:06:32.000Z","uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9eb11666d0ef3602714d58a2a55e4e0af65e9a9a","tid":61353,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:20:25.000Z","msg":"睇左hunter咁耐 一直想知比絲姬既真正實力係點<br />\n<br />\n好似到目前為止, 只係知佢會變大隻妹<br />\n但富奸都未令佢同真正勁既敵人打過<br />\n<br />\n唯一出左少少力打既好似只係貪婪島先果次 其餘時間都係同小剛 基路亞特訓 升LEVEL<br />\n<br />\n選新會長，黑暗大陸篇又變埋路人。本來以為黑暗大陸篇佢會有份去黑暗大陸，點知又係得個吉。<br />\n<br />\n真係好想睇下出盡全力同人打既比絲姬係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa2dbc078d3b84c37820354a0ed35ab971b15a5","tid":61353,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30a517e03c6aab4c4000260bdd376c6f04dff70","tid":61353,"uid":17994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:07:30.000Z","msg":"佢有上船喎"},{"pid":"688eb9dfc434a0eb200ebd98fb406afeceeb9982","tid":61353,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:28:11.000Z","msg":"應該低於預期<br />\n<br />\n協會啲人普遍廢<br />\n念能力喺戰鬥時唔知有冇用<br />\n身體質素係勁, 但未必勁過強化系"},{"pid":"ae86c1cb3d0d8f3bb0086b7d24c8432bc19126e3","tid":61353,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"佢係護衛之一wo"},{"pid":"462bb98637f799d319047d8b31b200645cb1641b","tid":61353,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:33:18.000Z","msg":"樓主可能化左灰都未必知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86159a09dfd0754f713558aac718269dd32ccf6","tid":61353,"uid":45672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-3