d":61353,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T09:49:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比絲姬應該揪唔贏會長、基爺、剛爸，但絕對揪得贏剛同基</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基仔招神速連護衛都跟唔到<br />\n比絲基邊有得打"},{"pid":"de810b76b3e75c4ed7d27fed385a8f98925edf64","tid":61353,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:27:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主應該連團長大戰畢索加都未睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岩岩追番晒<br />\n<br />\n團長大戰希索加真心正 但唔明點解希索加點復活同做乜鬼連其他旅團成員都追殺埋 仲要秒殺金毛仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外比絲姬都跟埋上船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但有冇機會比佢打呀? 又有古拿比加師傅, 十二支, 林友德, 金 等等<br />\n咁多角色一係就出黎為左要領便當<br />\n一係就要作得仲長過蟻篇<br />\n<br />\n已經未計到步去到黑暗大陸當地既情況已經咁多支線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁搞法會唔會仲耐過烙印由提及精靈界到去到精靈界既時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea574f63c330b829aa2fd13d486c4d43079e728","tid":61353,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:31:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比絲姬應該揪唔贏會長、基爺、剛爸，但絕對揪得贏剛同基</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基仔招神速連護衛都跟唔到<br />\n比絲基邊有得打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老老實實 我地跟本對比絲姬既戰鬥技能好似係一無所知咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係知佢會變大隻妹同美容能力<br />\n<br />\n而我好奇怪點解富奸出左呢個人物咁耐都唔對佢做番多啲詳細介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8ce6719f0de0bad6092332722ad750cf68e849","tid":61353,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:39:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新會長投票時小丑比分我記得比左佢95分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23eaf739df351f5107a6daee07b4185dd5add296","tid":61353,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主應該連團長大戰畢索加都未睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岩岩追番晒<br />\n<br />\n團長大戰希索加真心正 但唔明點解希索加點復活同做乜鬼連其他旅團成員都追殺埋 仲要秒殺金毛仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外比絲姬都跟埋上船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但有冇機會比佢打呀? 又有古拿比加師傅, 十二支, 林友德, 金 等等<br />\n咁多角色一係就出黎為左要領便當<br />\n一係就要作得仲長過蟻篇<br />\n<br />\n已經未計到步去到黑暗大陸當地既情況已經咁多支線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁搞法會唔會仲耐過烙印由提及精靈界到去到精靈界既時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢場大戰當時連載唔係好多人識欣賞，戰術太複雜少人明<br />\n但如果明就會發覺富奸用咗好多心思"},{"pid":"f4e202a57845ed5f3e73a7bb279b6ea7174fcf48","tid":61353,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T11:23:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>比絲姬應該揪唔贏會長、基爺、剛爸，但絕對揪得贏剛同基</blockquote><br />\n我估佢戰鬥力未及希索加、團長, 應該十二支、旅團入面中位級數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要唔要重睇GI食頭髮個段</blockquote><br />\n飛髮佬廢啫"},{"pid":"9eed630863f6fc2e6b11a0b57e8aaa6f7f914ef6","tid":61353,"uid":34,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T11:46:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新會長投票時小丑比分我記得比左佢95分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c5d6d1e8177e2e40d569433ef05b6301d00dae","tid":61353,"uid":34,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T11:47:21.000Z","msg":"基佬第一<br />\n蟻王第二<br />\n會長第三<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ade7c77b9b63ef4bbe7eefeef2287cb6dcdc08","tid":61353,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T11:56:25.000Z","msg":"每次講比絲姬就諗起呢本嘢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/e2n5Wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fe2n5Wz.jpg&h=05021fee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3acfd82055f70c3e32e2940ba4cdeb0c5e3013f","tid":61353,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T11:57:35.000Z","msg":"替身使者既實力唔會咁易比你睇得透"},{"pid":"3830c4fd2a1582b93c994767be32a847334568ef","tid":61353,"uid":10596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T13:48:55.000Z","msg":"相比起比絲姬....我反面仲想知排球佬實戰可以痴線成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dab3e566e28a35ab9820ff2f2b64cd2862be02e","tid":61353,"uid":10596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相比起比絲姬....我反面仲想知排球佬實戰可以痴線成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0640c896ede091619bc4b839471545c369b1fd2e","tid":61353,"uid":63053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T14:03:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相比起比絲姬....我反面仲想知排球佬實戰可以痴線成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n排球佬應該僅次於金<br />\n強如希索加都比佢屌打"},{"pid":"42d6a0ba205ae6ebc0b216b0118bd7e7d8f09838","tid":61353,"uid":63053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T14:06:44.000Z","msg":"比絲基戰鬥能力應該唔入流<br />\n變大隻只係變番原本個樣<br />\n只係靠基本身體能力"},{"pid":"9f5e2b2b948c4842fe88b1fef0e7ab57669c32a4","tid":61353,"uid":39559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T15:21:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比絲基戰鬥能力應該唔入流<br />\n變大隻只係變番原本個樣<br />\n只係靠基本身體能力</blockquote><br />\nhxh成日都強調強化系實戰最好<br />\n即係靠自己身體去戰鬥<br />\n咁比絲基變返大隻既話戰鬥能力點會唔入流呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a875daa250b3bfcdf973bbf62245462e8112f9","tid":61353,"uid":64598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講開又講，變大岡呢招係咪比絲姬教？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個制約，一個還原狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話呢？"},{"pid":"643e9d6ec96231d37f6518384c104cdefab6288a","tid":61353,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新會長投票時小丑比分我記得比左佢95分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n重睇啦邊有比分"},{"pid":"ecbf72c28e6145271bf908dfaac5a4ab6855631f","tid":61353,"uid":9292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T02:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新會長投票時小丑比分我記得比左佢95分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係比左基哥95分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似係"},{"pid":"d8d31237549f08dad72f6f0c2bbc5f429a9476eb","tid":61353,"uid":861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T03:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新會長投票時小丑比分我記得比左佢95分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係"},{"pid":"06ae65908e737fd3ac0dfc8c104dada17954c995","tid":61353,"uid":49481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T03:20:19.000Z","msg":"而家漫畫進度去到邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個時睇到d王子徵護衛"},{"pid":"af3f090f9fc73031a59faa43e993440d76373f69","tid":61353,"uid":69749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T04:55:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比絲姬應該揪唔贏會長、基爺、剛爸，但絕對揪得贏剛同基</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基仔招神速連護衛都跟唔到<br />\n比絲基邊有得打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實基路亞玩神速嘅話仲有無得輸<br />\n對付紅色護衛呢D頂級Level就話超厚防打唔入肉姐<br />\n對付普通人類Level可以電完再任打<br />\n好難想像有人會頂到"},{"pid":"bb8da003972819a996dbf21dd4c356037dffd008","tid":61353,"uid":16055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T05:58:19.000Z","msg":"目前睇到蟻王同會長打緊<br />\n覺得呢篇野係為左勁而勁咁<br />\n猶其比隻貓女念下就嚇到瀨屎<br />\n話曬都會長手下<br />\n而且主角雖然進步可以平衡返成個故事<br />\n但好似唔太自然<br />\n又唔知幾時封頂<br />\n<br />\n已經唔講動漫做得幾差<br />\n得個旁白講 好似睇小說咁"},{"pid":"5bd7b351c05de065da95de4a8603e3cb37ed87cf","tid":61353,"uid":16055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T06:04:42.000Z","msg":"雖然好想話邊個勁邊個勁<br />\n但講真無必要比較<br />\n因為佢地有時好打又要講戰術<br />\n講戰術又要講心態<br />\n又或者咩能力著數"},{"pid":"8cef6f8f509b100954d71f51d4f35b3bd0afde73","tid":61353,"uid":49280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T06:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>比絲姬應該揪唔贏會長、基爺、剛爸，但絕對揪得贏剛同基</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基仔招神速連護衛都跟唔到<br />\n比絲基邊有得打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老老實實 我地跟本對比絲姬既戰鬥技能好似係一無所知咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係知佢會變大隻妹同美容能力<br />\n<br />\n而我好奇怪點解富奸出左呢個人物咁耐都唔對佢做番多啲詳細介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老老實實,就算有神速都未必夠比絲基真面目打啦<br />\n比絲基身體能力定念嘅運用都高基路亞幾班<br />\n玩格鬥技嘅點會冇練過強化系,佢嘅硬應該硬到仆街<br />\n全力嘅話,一拳都已經打低基路亞,基路亞打幾十拳都未必打得贏佢"},{"pid":"818eaeef457cbf2c4b255a1863ecdbb919aebf77","tid":61353,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T09:54:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>目前睇到蟻王同會長打緊<br />\n覺得呢篇野係為左勁而勁咁<br />\n猶其比隻貓女念下就嚇到瀨屎<br />\n話曬都會長手下<br />\n而且主角雖然進步可以平衡返成個故事<br />\n但好似唔太自然<br />\n又唔知幾時封頂<br />\n<br />\n已經唔講動漫做得幾差<br />\n得個旁白講 好似睇小說咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n動定漫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇你用呢個膠term就知你幾多料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}